msgid "This is not a good place to release it."
msgstr "ここで放すのはよくない。"

msgid "There's nothing special behind the door."
msgstr "扉の裏には特に何もない。"

msgid "The door frame is about 15 centimeters thick."
msgstr "扉の枠の厚さは約15センチだ。"

msgid "Alright then..."
msgstr "よし、じゃあ……"

msgid "First, to take the real lily from the vase..."
msgstr "まず、本物の百合を花瓶から抜いて……"

msgid "Now... to make a paper lily from my letter..."
msgstr "それから……手紙で折り紙の百合を作って……"

msgid "And finally, to place it where the lily was."
msgstr "最後に、それをもともと百合があった場所に挿す。"

msgid "It seems like it worked."
msgstr "うまくいったみたい。"

msgid "You don't seem very impressed."
msgstr "あまり感動してないみたいだな。"

msgid "I suppose with everything that's happened so far, this is just another puzzle."
msgstr "今まであったことに比べたら、これもただのパズルでしょ。"

msgid "A puzzle, huh..."
msgstr "パズル、ね……"

msgid "I guess it's time to go home..."
msgstr "よし、帰ろう……"

msgid "The paper lily is in place."
msgstr "折り紙の百合が挿してある。"

msgid "(If I leave through here, the door might close...)"
msgstr "(ここから出たら、扉が閉じちゃうかも……)"

msgid "The door is open. A white light is coming through."
msgstr "開いた扉から白い光が差し込んでいる。"

msgid "Go through the door?"
msgstr "扉を抜ける？"

msgid "Yes"
msgstr "抜ける"

msgid "No"
msgstr "抜けない"

msgid "The door is locked."
msgstr "扉には鍵がかかっている。"
